simgui (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add Read SIM, Program SIM, and Batch Program workflow tabs.
  * Fix Debian packaging: use override_dh_auto_install for reliable installs.
  * Include simulator/data/ bundled test cards in package.
  * Install launcher directly as /usr/bin/simgui (no symlink).
  * Support pip --break-system-packages for Ubuntu 23.04+.

 -- SimGUI Developers <simgui@example.com>  Thu, 12 Mar 2026 12:00:00 +0000

simgui (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release.
  * CSV batch editor for SIM card configurations.
  * Card detection and ADM1 authentication via sysmo-usim-tool or pySim.
  * Built-in SIM programmer simulator with 20 real sysmoISIM-SJA5 profiles.
  * ICCID cross-verification safety check before ADM1 authentication.
  * Debian packaging for easy installation.

 -- SimGUI Developers <simgui@example.com>  Thu, 12 Mar 2026 12:00:00 +0000
